al%20governments%20levy%20property%20taxes%20to%20fund%20public%20services%20such%20as%20schools%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20fire%20and%20police%20protection%2C%20and%20other%20local%20services.%20And%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20live%2C%20they%20could%20make%20a%20serious%20difference%20in%20home%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmartAsset%20ranked%20342%20of%20the%20largest%20cities%20in%20the%20US%20to%20find%20where%20homeowners%20are%20paying%20the%20highest%20property%20taxes%20relative%20to%20home%20value%2C%20using%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Census%20Bureau's%202023%20American%20Community%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECities%20in%20the%20Northeast%20and%20Midwest%20tended%20to%20have%20the%20highest%20effective%20property%20tax%20rates%2C%20and%20several%20cities%20from%20Illinois%20and%20New%20York%20made%20the%20list.%20According%20to%20SmartAsset%2C%20Illinois%20has%20the%20second-highest%20property%20taxes%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20a%20statewide%20average%20effective%20tax%20rate%20of%202.1%25.%20That's%20more%20than%20twice%20the%20national%20average%20rate%20of%200.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cities%20in%20upstate%20New%20York%20also%20made%20the%20top%2010%20list.%20Since%20property%20taxes%20are%20set%20by%20the%20local%20municipality%2C%20there's%20high%20variability%20within%20the%20state.%20While%20New%20York%20City%20is%20infamous%20for%20its%20sky-high%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20property%20taxes%20in%20the%20city%20are%20actually%20in%20line%20with%20the%20national%20average%20of%200.9%25.%20SmartAsset%20found%20that%20Monroe%20County%2C%20located%20in%20upstate%20New%20York%2C%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20effective%20property%20tax%20rates%20in%20the%20state%2C%20at%202.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Texas%20city%20also%20made%20the%20list.%20While%20Texas%20is%20known%20for%20having%20no%20income%20tax%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20taxes%20are%20lower%20across%20the%20board%2C%20as%20Texas%20cities%20tend%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20property