t%20Perella%20Weinberg%20Partners%2C%20speaks%20during%20a%20Reuters%20Breakingviews%20panel%20in%20New%20York%2C%20U.S.%20January%2010%2C%202017.%20%20REUTERS%2FLucas%20Jackson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c37f7a75124c9281d0ec09f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeter%20Weinberg%2C%20Perella%20Chairman%3Cp%3EThomson%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c96470d6-0bfa-41f8-ad45-23ceeb6d9f6d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWords%20of%20wisdom%20for%20young%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Steel%2C%2073%2C%20has%20certainly%20earned%20the%20right%20to%20retire%2C%20he%20told%20BI%20he%20has%20zero%20interest%20in%20spending%20his%20days%20on%20a%20golf%20course%20or%20lounging%20at%20a%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20take%20time%20away%20over%20the%20holidays%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20nothing%20seems%20pretty%20uninteresting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20wear%20out%2C%20not%20rust%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20friends%20that%20are%20really%20happy%20at%20a%20different%20rhythm%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20judgments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteel%2C%20however%2C%20appreciates%20the%20flexibility%20the%20pandemic%20has%20introduced%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20including%20banking.%20Early%20on%20in%20his%20career%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20pressure%20behind%20constant%20face%20time%20was%2C%20at%20times%2C%20overkill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20'presentism'%20is%20maybe%20a%20bit%20overvalued.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20focused%2C%20committed%2C%20and%20available%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20that%20every%20day%20I%20had%20to%20be%20in%20before%20my%20boss%20and%20stay%20until%20after%20he%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20moderated%20a%20bit%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20main%20advice%20to%20young%20people%20is%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20and%20irreplaceable%20part%20of%20your%20company%20or%20team.%20He%20said%20you%20must%20think%20beyond%20the%20day-to-day%20tasks%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThinking%20about%20how%20what%20you're%20doing%20fits%20into%20a%20bigger%20picture%20and%20understanding%20that%20perspective%20is%20a%20good%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-steel-perella-weinberg-investment-banker-advising-blackrock-fink-alternatives-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738833301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a112c67bb3f854015b8aa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-steel-perella-weinberg-investment-banker-advising-blackrock-fink-alternatives-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Perella%20Weinberg's%20Bob%20Steel%20talks%20about%20his%20history%20with%20Larry%20Fink%2C%20BlackRock's%20expansion%20into%20alternative%20assets%2C%20and%20why%20he%20will%20never%20retire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ebrownstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Emmalyse%20Brownstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-steel-perella-weinberg-investment-banker-advising-blackrock-fink-alternatives-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deloitte%2C%20MEGA%20team%20up%20to%20drive%20digital%20transformation%20for%20Indian%20biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738833300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdeloitte-mega-team-up-to-drive-digital-transformation-for-indian-biz-125020600739_1.html%22%2