ss%20of%20deportation%20(by%20the%20US)%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20new...%20it%20has%20been%20there%20for%20years.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20policy%20applicable%20to%20only%20one%20country.%20Our%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20crackdown%20on%20illegal%20migrants%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20acknowledging%20also%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20engaging%20with%20the%20US%20to%20ensure%20deportees%20are%20not%20mistreated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20brief%20opening%20remarks%20were%20followed%20by%20a%20volley%20of%20questions%20and%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%20benches%2C%20including%20Trinamool%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20asking%20why%20the%20Indian%20government%20could%20not%20have%20sent%20a%20plane%20-%20military%20or%20civilian%20charter%20-%20to%20bring%20back%20its%20citizens%20in%20a%20more%20humane%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world...%20when%20countries%20like%20Colombia%2C%20which%20don't%20even%20figure%20in%20the%20top%2010%2C%20can%20send%20an%20aircraft%20and%20bring%20their%20citizens%20back%20with%20dignity%2C%20what%20stops%20our%20government%20from%20sending%20an%20aircraft%3F%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20shortage%20of%20these...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20specifically%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgly1we7gx4o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColombia%20and%20its%20stand-off%20with%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20flights%20to%20the%20South%20American%20country%20were%20also%20US%20military%20aircraft%20on%20which%20too%20deportees%20were%20shackled%2C%20prompting%20furious%20protests%20from%20Colombian%20President%20Gustavo%20Petro%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20let%20any%20more%20such%20flights%20land%20in%20his%20country.%20The%20US%20responded%20by%20slapping%2025%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20Colombia%2C%20which%20then%20agreed%20to%2