eepseek-openai-america-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek's%20R1%20AI%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20was%20released%20on%20January%2020.%20He's%20been%20using%20AI%20tools%20like%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-deep-research-launch-chatgpt-ai-agent-deepseek-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20analyze%20code%20and%20draft%20emails%2C%20which%20saves%20him%20time%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Nethala%20said%20R1%20wasn't%20as%20helpful%20for%20less%20technical%20questions%2C%20such%20as%20random%20inquiries.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20said%20ChatGPT%20remains%20his%20go-to%20tool%20for%20%26quot%3Brandom%20questions%20and%20brainstorming%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-computer-use-ai-explainer-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20best%20bet%20when%20he%20wants%20%26quot%3Bmore%20thoughtful%20analysis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20is%20like%20that%20brilliant%20friend%20who's%20fantastic%20at%20math%20but%20not%20for%20generic%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nethala%2C%2033%2C%20who's%20based%20in%20Illinois.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20myself%20switching%20between%20tools%20based%20on%20what%20I'm%20doing%2C%20kind%20of%20like%20picking%20the%20right%20screwdriver%20for%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20workers%20told%20BI%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-r1-open-source-replicate-ai-west-china-hugging-face-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek's%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20generally%20performs%20well%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20free%20is%20a%20major%20perk%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20it%20seems%20to%20trail%20behind%20its%20AI%20competitors%20in%20some%20areas.%20These%20individuals%20regularly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-use-ai-save-time-work-best-ways-use-chatgpt-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse%20other%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20draft%20emails%2C%20summarize%20documents%2C%20improve%20code%2C%20and%20write%20content%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20boost%20their%20productivity%20and%20make%20their%20jobs%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20ChatGPT%2C%20Claude%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20market%20have%20free%20and%20paid%20versions%2C%20which%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoffer%20different%20access%20options.%20For%20example%2C%20ChatGPT's%20paid%20version%20costs%20%2420%20monthly%20and%20extends%20limits%20on%20file%20uploads%2C%20advanced%20data%20analysis%2C%20and%20image%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227028b259-8f67-4eae-ac57-c7a79fa09738%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorkers%20like%20DeepSeek's%20low%20cost%20and%20open-source%20nature%2C%20but%20are%20iffy%20on%20its%20writing%20skills%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Benson-May%20works%20full-time%20as%20an%20accountant%20and%20writes%20a%20newsletter%20about%20entrepreneurs%20in%20his%20spare%20time.%20At%20his%20accounting%20job%2C%20he%20said%20he%20uses%20the%20paid%20versions%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20Claude%20to%20draft%20emails%20and%20summarize%20documents.%20For%20his%20newsletter%2C%20he%20uses%20the%20tools%20to%20help%20write%20articles%2C%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20headlines%2C%20and%20website%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenson-May%20said%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20AI%20model%20is%20fairly%20comparable%20to%20ChatGPT%20but%20he's%20noticed%20some%20differences.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20said%20R1%20is%20great%20at%20writing%20articles%20and%20h