0victim.%20This%20form%20of%20attack%20highlights%20the%20growing%20risks%20of%20spyware%20and%20how%20users%20can%20be%20unknowingly%20targeted%20without%20any%20action%20on%20their%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WhatsApp%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EReuters%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20users%20were%20sent%20malicious%20electronic%20documents%20that%20required%20no%20user%20interaction%20to%20compromise%20their%20targets%2C%20a%20so-called%20zero-click%20hack%20that%20is%20considered%20particularly%20stealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHackers%20targets%20were%20journalists%20and%20civil%20society%20members%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EReuters%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20WhatsApp%20officials%20declined%20to%20say%20who%2C%20specifically%2C%20was%20targeted.%20But%20he%20said%20those%20targeted%20were%20based%20in%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20countries%2C%20including%20several%20people%20in%20Europe.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2025%2Fjan%2F31%2Fwhatsapp-israel-spyware%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20hackers%20targets%20were%20journalists%20and%20members%20of%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20WhatsApp%20had%20since%20disrupted%20the%20hacking%20effort%20and%20was%20referring%20targets%20to%20Canadian%20internet%20watchdog%20group%20Citizen%20Lab.%20The%20official%20declined%20to%20discuss%20how%20it%20determined%20that%20Paragon%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20hack.%20He%20said%20law%20enforcement%20and%20industry%20partners%20had%20been%20informed%20but%20declined%20to%20give%20details.%20The%20FBI%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20message%20seeking%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizen%20Lab%20researcher%20John%20Scott-Railton%20said%20the%20discovery%20of%20Paragon%20spyware%20targeting%20WhatsApp%20users%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20reminder%20that%20mercenary%20spyware%20continues%20to%20proliferate%2C%20a