0%C2%A0Awami%20League%20party's%20Facebook%20account%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20they%20fear%20a%20house%3F%20We%20live%20for%20those%20memories%20of%20Dhanmondi...%20Last%20time%20they%20set%20this%20house%20on%20fire%2C%20now%20they%20are%20destroying%20it.%20Have%20I%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20this%20country%3F%20Then%20why%20such%20disrespect%3F%20The%20only%20memory%20that%20both%20my%20sister%20and%20I%20have%20clung%20to%20is%20being%20wiped%20out...%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20my%20people%20who%20is%20behind%20this.%20I%20want%20justice...%20A%20structure%20can%20be%20erased%2C%20but%20history%20cannot%20be%20wiped%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20emotional%20Hasina%2C%20who%20sounded%20like%20she%20was%20in%20tears%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fawamileague.1949%252Fvideos%252F934742535395405%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ousted%20Premier%20warned%20the%20opponents%20must%20remember%20that%20history%20takes%20its%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20group%20of%20protesters%20vandalised%20and%20set%20on%20fire%20to%20Bangabandhu%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman's%20residence%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20Wednesday%20during%20Hasina's%20live%20online%20address%20organised%20by%20the%20Awami%20League's%20now-disbanded%20student%20wing%20Chhatra%20League.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20several%20thousand%20people%20rallied%20in%20front%20of%20the%20house%20in%20the%20capital's%20Dhanmondi%20area%20since%20early%20evening%20following%20a%20social%20media%20call%20for%20a%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BBulldozer%20Procession%26quot%3B%20as%20Hasina%20was%20supposed%20to%20make%20her%20address%20at%209%20pm%20(BST).%20The%20house%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20iconic%20symbol%20in%20Bangladesh's%20history%20as%20Mujibur%20largely%20led%20the%20pre-independence%20autonomy%20movement%20for%20decades%20from%20the%20residence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHasina%20said%20she%20and%20her%20only%20surviving%20sibling%20had%20donated%20their%20ancestral%20house%20to%20a%20trust%20as%20public%20property%2C%20turning%20the%20building%20into%20the%20Bangabandhu%20Memorial%20Museum%2C%20as%20Sheikh%20Mujib%20was%20fondly%20called%20%26quot%3BBangabandhu%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BFriend%20of%20Bengal%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20late%201960s%20when%20his%20movement%20for%20autonomy%20from%20Pakistan%20turned%20into%20a%20mass%20upheaval%20in%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2032%20Dhanmondi%20residence%20was%20also%20set%20on%20fire%20earlier%20on%20August%205%20last%20year%20when%20Hasina's%20nearly%2016-year%20Awami%20League%20regime%20was%20toppled%20and%20she%20secretly%20left%20the%20country%20along%20with%20her%20younger%20sister%20Sheikh%20Rehana%20for%20India%20on%20a%20Bangladesh%20Air%20Force%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20address%2C%20Hasina%20also%20called%20upon%20the%20countrymen%20to%20organise%20a%20resistance%20against%20the%20current%20regime.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20yet%20to%20have%20the%20strength%20to%20destroy%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20independence%20that%20we%20earned%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20martyrs%20with%20a%20bulldozer%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasina%20said%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Nobel%20Laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus's%20incumbent%20regime%2C%20installed%20by%20the%20Anti-Discrimination%20Students%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20movement%20earlier%20promised%20to%20scrap%20Bangladesh's%201972%20Constitution%20as%20they%20promised%20to%20bury%20the%20%26quot%3BMujibist%20constitution%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20some%20far-right%20groups%20also%20suggested%20a%20change%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20adopted%20by%20the%20Sheikh%20Mujib-led%20post-independence%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20mentioned%20past%20assassination%20attempts%20on%20her%20life%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Allah%20has%20kept%20me%20alive%20through%20all%20this%2C%20there%20must%20be%20some%20work%20left%20for%20me.%20Otherwise%2C%20how%20could%20I%20have%20escaped%20death%20so%20many%20times%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20direct%20accusation%2C%20she%20suggested%20that%20the%20current%20Muhammad%20Yunus-led%20regime%20orchestrated%20an%20alleged%20plot%20to%20eliminate%20her%20and%20her%20family.%20%26quot%3BThe%20meticulous%20plan%20by%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20this%20time%20was%20to%20kill%20me%20and%20my%20sister%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20criticising%20Yunus%2C%20Hasina%20stressed%20that%20during%20her%20regime%2C%20she%20had%20helped%20his%20Grameen%20Bank%20and%20its%20ventures%20with%20funding%20of%20400%20crore%20Bangladeshi%20taka.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20entire%20amount%20was%20laundered.%20Bangladesh%20is%20suffering%20due%20to%20one%20man's%20personal%20ambitions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20speech%2C%20Hasina%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20ordinary%20students%20were%20used%20by%20Yunus%20for%20an%20orchestrated%20movement%20to%20grab%20the%20state%20power%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20studies%20to%20build%20their%20future%20to%20serve%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20age%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20be%20manipulated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20hinting%20that%20young%20minds%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20manipulation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738830000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fsji5m61_sheikh-hasina-crying-_625x300_18_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcant-erase-history-sheikh-hasinas-tearful-message-after-mob-vandalises-fathers-house-in-dhaka-7646940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20m