%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20policy%20to%20tighten%20the%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%2C%20they%20have%20narrated%20the%20treacherous%20trek%20through%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%20'Donkey'%20route%20to%20reach%20the%20US.%20They%20shared%20how%20their%20American%20Dream%20was%20shattered%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20and%20they%20were%20handcuffed%20and%20put%20on%20the%20return%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military's%20C-17%20Globemaster%20aircraft%2C%20in%20which%20they%20were%20packed%20off%20for%20home%2C%20landed%20in%20Amritsar%20yesterday%20with%20104%20deportees%20-%20all%20Indians.%20The%20C-17%20aircraft%20runs%20an%20extremely%20high%20cost%20when%20compared%20to%20even%20first-class%20and%20chartered%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week's%20flight%20to%20Guatemala%2C%20for%20example%2C%20had%20likely%20incurred%20a%20cost%20of%20%244%2C675%20per%20migrant%2C%20five%20times%20%24853%2C%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20one-way%20first%20class%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%20The%20cost%20was%20also%20significantly%20higher%20than%20commercial%20charter%20flights%20that%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20hired%20for%20previous%20deportation%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deportations%20come%20amid%20Trump's%20crackdown%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20right%20after%20taking%20over%20as%20the%20US%20President.%20The%20US%20government%20had%20earlier%20flown%20back%20immigrants%20to%20Guatemala%2C%20Peru%2C%20and%20Honduras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%20Of%20Deportation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20deporting%2064%20migrants%20to%20Guatemala%20on%20the%20C-17%20aircraft%20was%20around%20%2428%2C500%20per%20hour%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20an%20unnamed%20US%20official%20as%20saying.%20The%20flight%20took%20about%2010.5%20hours%20to%20complete%20the%20journey.%20This%20excluded%20any%20ground%20time%20or%20time%20taken%20to%20prepare%20for%20take-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plane%20flying%20from%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas%20to%20Amritsar%20takes%20over%2019%20flight%20hours%20with%20multiple%20stops.%20Based%20on%20the%20above%20figure%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20operating%20the%20giant%20transport%20aircraft%20calculates%20to%20over%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%2C%20or%20over%20Rs%204%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20round%20of%20deportation%20of%20Indians%20comes%20amid%20reports%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20may%20visit%20the%20US%20next%20week.%20India%20and%20the%20US%20have%20identified%2018%2C000-odd%20Indian%20illegal%20migrants%20who%20may%20face%20deportation%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20said%20PM%20Modi%20has%20assured%20him%20of%20taking%20back%20the%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20stating%20that%20India%20%26quot%3Bwill%20do%20what's%20right%26quot%3B.%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20too%2C%20has%20indicated%20that%20India%20is%20open%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%20return%26quot%3B%20of%20Indians%20who%20are%20living%20illegally%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Cost%20Has%20Risen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20sending%20back%20the%20migrants%20on%20a%20C-17%20Globemaster%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20chartering%20a%20commercial%20aircraft%20by%20the%20ICE.%20It%20usually%20charters%20Boeing%20737%20or%20McDonnell%20Douglas%20MD-80%20series%20planes%20for%20deportation%2C%20but%20the%20US%20government%20is%20now%20using%20military%20aircraft%20to%20send%20back%20the%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20hiring%20charter%20planes%20has%20varied%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20%26quot%3BICE%20Air%26quot%3B%20flights%20were%20priced%20at%20%248%2C577%20per%20flight%20hour%20back%20in%202021.%20But%20a%202023%20flight%20carrying%20135%20deportees%20that%20lasted%20about%20five%20hours%20incurred%20a%20cost%20of%20%2417%2C000%20per%20flight%20hour%2C%20t