%3EDeception%20and%20Hardship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20migrants%20had%20spent%20vast%20sums%20-%20often%20obtained%20through%20loans%20-%20on%20promises%20of%20legal%20entry%20into%20the%20US.%20Instead%2C%20they%20endured%20gruelling%2C%20multi-country%20treks%20arranged%20by%20human%20traffickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaspal%20Singh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20from%20Punjab's%20Gurdaspur%2C%20was%20among%20those%20deported.%20He%20said%20he%20paid%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20to%20an%20agent%20who%20promised%20him%20legal%20passage%20to%20the%20US.%20He%20first%20flew%20to%20Brazil%2C%20where%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20journey%20would%20also%20be%20by%20air.%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20the%20dangerous%20%26quot%3Bdonkey%20route%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20illegal%20and%20often%20perilous%20path%20used%20by%20traffickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20spent%20six%20months%20in%20Brazil%20before%20attempting%20to%20cross%20into%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20US%20Border%20Patrol%20on%20January%2024%20and%20detained%20for%2011%20days.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20no%20idea%20we%20were%20being%20deported%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20we%20were%20being%20moved%20to%20another%20detention%20center.%20Then%20they%20told%20us%20we%20were%20going%20back%20to%20India.%20We%20were%20handcuffed%20and%20our%20legs%20were%20chained%20until%20we%20landed%20in%20Amritsar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarwinder%20Singh%2C%20from%20Punjab's%20Hoshiarpur%2C%20paid%20Rs%2042%20lakh%20to%20an%20agent%2C%20and%20was%20taken%20through%20multiple%20countries%3A%20Qatar%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Peru%2C%20Colombia%2C%20Panama%2C%20Nicaragua%2C%20and%20Mexico.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20walked%20for%20days%2C%20crossed%20mountains%2C%20and%20nearly%20drowned%20in%20the%20sea%2C%26quot%3B%20Harwinder%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20one%20man%20die%20in%20the%20Panama%20jungle%20and%20another%20drown%20at%20sea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20crossed%2017-18%20hills.%20If%20one%20person%20slipped%2C%20there%20was%20no%20chance%20of%20survival.%20If%20anyone%20got%20injured%2C%20they%20were%20left%20to%20die.%20We%20saw%20dead%20bodies%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20migrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20migrants%2C%20the%20financial%20burden%20is%20as%20devastating%20as%20the%20emotional%20toll.%20Many%20families%20took%20out%20massive%20loans%2C%20mortgaged%20their%20homes%2C%20or%20borrowed%20from%20relatives%2C%20expecting%20their%20loved%20ones%20to%20secure%20well-paying%20jobs%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Cost%20of%20Deportation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20a%20recent%20military%20flight%20deporting%20migrants%20to%20Guatemala%20likely%20cost%20at%20least%20Rs%204%2C09%2C331%20(%244%2C675)%20per%20person%20-%20more%20than%20five%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20one-way%20first-class%20ticket%20on%20American%20Airlines%20for%20the%20same%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement's%20(ICE)%20standard%20chartered%20deportation%20flights%20cost%20Rs%2014%2C88%2C527%20(%2417%2C000)%20per%20flight%20hour%2C%20with%20a%20typical%20flight%20carrying%20135%20deportees%20and%20lasting%20five%20hours.%20This%20translates%20to%20roughly%20Rs%2055%2C163%20(%24630)%20per%20person%2C%20assuming%20the%20charter%20company%20absorbs%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20return%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-17%20transport%20aircraft%20used%20for%20deportations%20has%20an%20estimated%20operational%20cost%20of%20Rs%2024%2C95%2C388%20(%2428%2C500)%20per%20hour.%20Given%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%20this%20latest%20deportation%20flight%20is%20likely%20the%20most%20expensive%20one%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20ICE%20charters%20commercial%20flights%20for%20such%20operations.%20However%2C%20under%20President%20Trump%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20visible%20shift%20toward%20military%20aircraft%20for%20high-profile%20deportations%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20framed%20illegal%20immigration%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binvasion%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20described%20undocumented%20migrants%20as%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Baliens.%26quot%3B%20The%20optics%20of%20migrants%20being%20loaded%20onto%20massive%20military%20planes%20also%20sends%20a%20hardline%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20Action%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%2C%20the%20migrants%20were%20questioned%20by%20multiple%20agencies%2C%20including%20Punjab%20Police%20and%20central%20intelligence%20authorities%2C%20to%20verify%20any%20criminal%20records.%20The%20deportations%20come%20just%20days%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Washington%2C%20where%20immigration%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20key%20topic%20in%20talks%20with%20President%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20were%20adjourned%20till%20noon%20today%20after%20a%20political%20uproar%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20deportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20matter%20is%20with%20the%20government.%20This%20is%20the%20matter%20of%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%20This%20subject%20is%20related%20to%20another%20country.%20Government%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20it.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20not%20to%20resort%20to%20planned%20disruptions%20to%20prevent%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20House.%20Question%20Hour%20is%20an%20important%20session%20where%20members%20put%20forward%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20citizens%20and%20the%20government%20answer%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20amid%20controversy%20over%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738824840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fbceh67mo_indian-migrants-deported-reuters-_625x300_06_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-handcuffed-chained-thrown-like-boxes-indian-migrants-american-nightmare-7646326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20migrants%2C%20hailing%20from%20various%20Indian%20states%2C%20were%20rounded%20up%20in%20a%20sweeping%20crackdown%20on%20illegal%20immigration.%20Among%20them%2C%2033%20were%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%2030%20from%20Punjab%2C%20three%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20two%20from%20Chandigarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrants-deported-handcuffed-chained-thrown-like-boxes-indian-migrants-american-nightmare-7646326%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Named%20For%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20Aus%20Star%20Announces%20ODI%20Retirement%3A%20%26quot%3BFocus%20On...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20seam-bowling%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Marcus%20Stoinis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F42327-marcus-peter-stoinis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMarcus%20Stoinis%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20surprisingly%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20ODIs%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20bringing%20the%20end%20of%20his%20international%2050-over%20career%20at%2074%20games.%20Cricket%20Australia%20(CA)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Stoinis%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20available%20for%20selection%20in%20T20Is%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20the%2050-over%20format%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20T20%20cricket.%20Stoinis'%20retirement%20from%20ODIs%20also%20means%20CA%20will%20replace%20him%20with%20another%20player%20in%20Australia's%20squ