tural%20leader%2C%20an%20exceptionally%20popular%20player%20and%20a%20great%20person.%20He%20should%20be%20congratulated%20on%20his%20ODI%20career%20and%20all%20of%20his%20achievements%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20head%20coach%20Andrew%20McDonald.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Stoinis%20retiring%20from%20ODIs%20just%20a%20fortnight%20before%20Champions%20Trophy%20begins%2C%20along%20with%20injury%20concerns%20over%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Josh%20Hazlewood%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1040-josh-hazlewood-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJosh%20Hazlewood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CA%20said%20the%20National%20Selection%20Panel%20(NSP)%20will%20finalise%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20Champion's%20Trophy%20following%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20have%20already%20lost%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Marsh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1425-mitchell-marsh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Marsh%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20a%20back%20injury%2C%20and%20Stoinis'%20exit%20from%20ODIs%20means%20they%20need%20to%20fill%20in%20four%20places%20in%20their%2015-man%20squad%20for%20the%20eight-team%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20have%20time%20until%20February%2012%20to%20submit%20their%20final%20squads%20of%2015%20for%20the%20tournament%20to%20the%20ICC.%20Australia%20are%20drawn%20in%20Group%20B%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20alongside%20Afghanistan%2C%20England%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738824480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%