22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Modi-Trump%20Meet%3A%20Don't%20Fall%20For%20Window%20Dressing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20hectic%20activity%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20as%20reports%20point%20to%20a%20visit%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20Washington%20in%20just%20a%20week.%20That's%20unusual.%20Normally%2C%20an%20event%20of%20this%20magnitude%20would%20take%20months%20of%20preparation%20by%20both%20sides.%20A%20White%20House%20%E2%80%98official'%20has%20even%20confirmed%20that%20Modi%20will%20visit%20the%20US%20on%20February%2012%2C%20meeting%20the%20President%20the%20next%20day.%20True%2C%20there%20already%20had%20been%20rumours%20of%20Modi%20possibly%20making%20a%20trip%20to%20Washington%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20scheduled%20visit%20to%20Paris%20to%20co-chair%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Action%20Summit.%20So%20far%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Ministry%20has%20been%20quiet%20on%20the%20Washington%20visit%2C%20even%20as%20a%20hail%20of%20preparatory%20actions%20are%20evident%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIrritants%20Upfront%3A%20Dollars%20And%20Such%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20winds%20did%20not%20seem%20good.%20As%20President-elect%2C%20Trump%20was%20threatening%20tariffs%20against%20the%20BRICS%20(Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20South%20Africa)%20grouping%2C%20demanding%20that%20they%20abandon%20any%20talk%20of%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20dollar%20and%20having%20a%20separate%20currency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20fear%20is%20not%20insubstantial.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20group%20has%20expanded%20to%20include%20Iran%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Ethiopia%20and%20Egypt%2C%20and%20some%2034%20countries%20have%20submitted%20an%20expression%20of%20interest%20in%20joining%20the%20bloc%20of%20major%20emerging%20economies.%20Imposing%20tariffs%20against%20all%20of%20them%20would%20indeed%20be%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20any%20move%20towards%20de-dollarisation%20is%20certain%20to%20invite%20some%20form%20of%20American%20retribution.%20Until%20recently%2C%20nearly%20100%25%20of%20oil%20trading%20was%20conducted%20in%20US%20dollars.%20But%2C%20in%202023%2C%20a%20fifth%20of%20oil%20trade%20was%20reportedly%20done%20under%20non-US%20dollar%20currencies%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%20%E2%80%98unit'%E2%80%94if%20it%20materialises%E2%80%94will%20be%20backed%20by%20a%20basket%20of%20currencies%20of%20the%20respective%20member%20countries.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20yuan%20will%20be%20the%20strongest.%20This%20is%20a%20reality%20that%20hardly%20serves%20Delhi's%20interests.%20Foreign%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20has%20since%20denied%20the%20possibility%20of%20any%20backing%20of%20such%20steps%2C%20indicating%20that%20it%20is%20neither%20%E2%80%98policy'%20nor%20'strategy'%20to%20consider%20de-dollarisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20move%20number%20one%2C%20and%20a%20very%20swift%20one%20indicating%20that%20in%20a%20consensus-based%20grouping%2C%20India%20will%20stand%20aligned%20with%20US%20interests%2C%20at%20least%20in%20this%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Deportation%20Spree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20concern%20is%20the%20Trumpian%20threat%20to%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20the%20weaponising%20of%20tariffs%2C%20which%20saw%20Columbia%20first%20putting%20up%20a%20fight%20but%20then%20caving%20in%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours%2C%20agreeing%20to%20take%20back%20all%20undocumented%20migrants.%20China%20bowed%2C%20too%2C%20as%20nearly%20five%20flights%20sent%20back%20undocumented%20Chinese%20immigrants%20from%20America.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20however%2C%20was%20quick%20off%20the%20mark%2C%20with%20Jaishankar%20in%20his%20press%20interaction%20noting%20that%20while%20Delhi%20wanted%20%E2%80%98legal%20mobility'%20for%20its%20citizens%2C%20it%20was%20against%20illegal%20migration%20and%20all%20the%20other%20related%20threats%20it%20entails.%20The%20issue%20was%20clearly%20raised%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20as%20a%20read-out%20confirmed.%20It%20was%20broached%20%E2%80%98gently'%2C%20with%20the%20main%20text%20stressing%20continuing%20cooperation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20India%20confirmed%20that%20it%20was%20taking%20back%2018%2C000%20identified%20migrants%2C%20with%20some%20205%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20Amritsar%2C%20even%20as%20orders%20were%20given%20to%20ensure%20that%20bureaucratic%20procedures%20were%20in%20place.%20The%20trouble%20is%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20where%20that%20came%20from.%20Last%20year%2C%20US%20data%20indicated%20that%20some%2090%2C105%20people%20were%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20country%20illegally%2C%20with%20Indians%20totalling%20some%203%25%20of%20them.%20That's%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20an%20issue%20that%20can%20be%20resolved%20easily%20or%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThose%20Pesky%20Tariffs%20Don't%20Exist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20unveiled%20Union%20budget%20also%20made%20some%20significant%20announcements%2C%20again%20pre-empting%20America's%20tariff%20threats.%20It%20did%20away%20with%20peak%20tariff%20rates%20of%20150%25%2C%20125%25%20and%20100%25%20on%20imports.%20These%20actually%20applied%20to%20just%20five%20items%2C%20including%20the%20contentious%20Harley%20Davidson%20motorcycles%20and%20imported%20Tesla%20cars%20(as%20well%20as%20Japanese%20vehicles%20and%20other%20bikes).%20While%20duties%20have%20been%20slashed%2C%20a%20cess%20remains%2C%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20Centre.%20This%20can%20be%20used%20flexibly%20at%20any%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20import%20duties%20on%20the%20top%2030%20items%20exported%20by%20the%20US%20to%20India%E2%80%94crude%20oil%2C%20coking%20coal%2C%20aeroplanes%2C%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20(already%20minimal)%20being%20the%20top%20ones%E2%80%94are%20anyway%20in%20the%20range%20of%20zero%20to%207.5%25.%20All%20this%20is%20very%20good%20optics%2C%20with%20the%20data%20apparently%20shared%20with%20US%20officials%2C%20and%20the%20message%20going%20out%20that%20India%20is%20not%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98high%20tariff'%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20Then%2C%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20messages%20from%20Washington%20were%20also%20many%2C%20with%20Jaishankar%20being%20the%20first%20top%20diplomat%20to%20meet%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20and%20the%20scheduling%20of%20the%20Quad%20foreign%20ministers'%20meeting%20immediately%20after%20the%20inauguration%20being%20seen%20as%20Trump%20reinforcing%20his%20backing%20of%20the%20grouping.%20That's%20also%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20China%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20which%20analysts%20seem%20to%20have%20missed%20amid%20all%20the%20bonhomie%20seen%20in%20the%20call%20between%20President%20Xi%20and%20Trump%E2%80%94in%20which%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latter's%20tweet%2C%20Xi%20promised%20to%20work%20for%20a%20peaceful%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWords%2C%20however%2C%20are%20cheap.%20True%2C%20with%20Trump%20promising%20to%20%E2%80%98take%20over'%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20Israel's%20Netanyahu%20recently%2C%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change.%20True%20also%20that%20Trump%20is%20to%20call%20the%20Chinese%20President%20soon%E2%80%94this%20after%20he%20promised%2060%25%20tariffs%20against%20Beijing%20but%20ultimately%20imposed%20a%20mere%2010%25.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20these%20tariffs%20are%20actually%20linked%20to%20narcotics%20trafficking%2C%20something%20Beijing%20too%20sees%20as%20a%20threat%20rather%20than%20trade.%20China%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20fired%20off%20the%20launch%20of%20DeepSeek%20immediately%20after%2C%20which%20topped%20download%20charts%20and%20wiped%20billions%20of%20dollars%20off%20the%20market%20of%20Nvidia%2C%20sending%20the%20signal%20that%20the%20country%20can%20retaliate%20in%20multiple%20ways.%20The%20actual%20retaliation%20by%20Beijing%20in%20terms%20of%20tariffs%20was%20relatively%20mild%20in%20hard%20terms.%20Expect%20more%20negotiation%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Unchanging%20Constant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20is%20not%20open%20to%20negotiation%20is%20one%20constant%20in%20the%20US%20National%20Security%20Strategy%3A%20it%20states%20unambiguously%20that%20the%20US%20doesn't%20tolerate%20competitors%20or%20challenges%20from%20other%20powers.%20This%20was%20Trump's%20outlook%2C%20too%2C%20in%202017%2C%20and%20it%20will%20likely%20be%20even%20more%20magnified%20now.%20A%20rising%20China%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated.%20And%20Trump%2C%20being%20what%20he%20is%2C%20will%20want%20other%20powers%20to%20step%20up.%20That%20includes%20not%20just%20allies%2C%20but%20also%20%E2%80%98friends'%20like%20India.%20Prepare%20to%20step%20up%20to%20the%20plate%2C%20with%E2%80%94as%20the%20White%20House%20readout%20made%20clear%E2%80%94more%20weapons%20buys%20from%20the%20US.%20%E2%80%98Strategic%20autonomy'%20is%20going%20to%20get%20more%20difficult%20to%20maintain%2C%20at%20least%20in%20terms%20of%20managing%20Beijing's%20perceptions.%20The%20point%2C%20ultimately%2C%20is%20that%20China%20is%20going%20to%20be%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20US%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20this%20can%20be%20a%20huge%20opportunity.%20The%20proposed%20US-India%20Defence%20Cooperation%20Act%202024%2C%20introduced%20by%20Rubio%2C%20back%20then%20a%20Senator%2C%20is%20an%20example.%20It%20treats%20India%20at%20par%20with%20US%20allies%2C%20placing%20it%20on%20nearly%20the%20same%20footing%20as%20them%20in%20NATO%20(North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Organisation)%20in%20terms%20of%20provision%20of%20defence%20equipment.%20On%20the%20question%20of%20transfer%20of%20technology%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20at%20present.%20This%20point%20will%20need%20to%20be%20added%20to%20a%20future%20proposal%20to%20make%20it%20attractive%20to%20India%20and%20to%20boost%20not%20just%20the%20Indian%20defence%20industry%20but%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20on%20which%20everything%20else%20rests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20these%20additions%20will%20need%20a%20Trumpian%20heave%20to%20get%20past%20Washington%20bureaucracy%E2%80%94something%20the%20US%20President%20is%20already%20battling%20with.%20The%20question%20now%20is%2C%20is%20the%20US%20President%20convinced%20that%20a%20strong%20India%20is%20in%20America's%20interests%3F%20And%2C%20is%20India%20ready%20to%20go%20the%20whole%20hog%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20in%20specific%20military%20terms%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20the%20two%20key%20questions%2C%20and%20on%20them%20will%20depend%20much%20of%20the%20friendship%20between%20US%20and%20India.%20The%20rest%20is%20merely%20window%20dressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tara%20Kartha%20is%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20Secretariat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738821480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2F2lenoa3g_pm-modi-donald-trump-houston-pti_625x300_23_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-trump-meet-dont-fall-for-window-dressing-7646079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20rising%20China%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated.%20And%20Trump%2C%20being%20what%20he%20is%2C%20will%20want%20other%20powers%20to%20step%20up.%20That%20includes%20not%20just%20allies%2C%20but%20also%20'friends'%20like%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-trump-meet-dont-fall-for-window-dressing-7646079%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22