0%26quot%3BHow%20Leaders%20Lead%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20which%20aired%20on%20January%2030.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20my%20wife%20would%20have%20gone%20with%20me%2C%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20added%20that%20the%20presidency%20means%20%26quot%3Bsubjecting%20your%20family%20to%20some%20very%20tough%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20prepared%20for%20that%2C%20I%20was%20unprepared%20for%20it%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20said%20that%20while%20he%20%26quot%3Bwould%20never%20rule%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20running%20for%20president%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20him%20because%20of%20other%20reasons%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20there%20are%20skills%20that%20people%20have%20in%20the%20business%20world%20that%20may%20translate%20to%20the%20political%20world%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20mistake%20to%20automatically%20think%20that's%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20didn't%20think%20he%20had%20the%20necessary%20political%20skills%20to%20make%20the%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20on%20top%20of%20the%20experience%20one%20should%20accrue%20from%20smaller%20political%20appointments%20before%20gunning%20for%20the%20presidency%2C%20Dimon%20told%20Novak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20literally%20think%20you%20should%20kind%20of%20have%20a%20warm-up%20before%20you%20go%20for%20president.%20A%20warm-up%20could%20be%20Congress%2C%20or%20Senate%2C%20or%20governor%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20people%20learn%20those%20skills%20before%20you%20go%20for%20the%20big%20enchilada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20for%20president%20would%20also%20mean%20having%20to%20give%20up%20his%20job%20at%20JPMorgan%2C%20which%20he%20enjoys%2C%20Dimon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20damn%20proud%20of%20it%20so%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20I%20add%20a%20lot%20here.%20I'd%20be%20giving%20that%20up%20for%20kind%20of