nnouncement%20after%20an%20hourlong%20court%20hearing%2C%20during%20which%20a%20government%20lawyer%20said%20only%20two%20Musk%20allies%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20them%20now%20Treasury%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20had%20any%20access%20to%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20contention%20was%20met%20with%20skepticism%20from%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20seeking%20to%20ensure%20the%20data's%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20concerned%20that%20the%20records%20%E2%80%94%20the%20personal%20information%20of%20our%20association's%20members%20%E2%80%94%20are%20still%20compromised%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20lawyer%2C%20Nandan%20Joshi%2C%20who%20represents%20three%20unions%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Treasury%20Secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funion-groups-sue-accuse-treasury-giving-doge-access-data-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScott%20Bessent%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20a%20compromise%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20unbreak%20the%20egg%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreasury%20officials%20have%20so%20far%20not%20been%20forthcoming%20on%20what%20access%20the%20two%20Musk%20allies%20have%20to%20the%20data%2C%20Joshi%20told%20the%20judge.%20The%20two%20were%20identified%20in%20court%20as%20Cloud%20Software%20Group%20CEO%20Tom%20Krause%20and%20Marko%20Elez%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20SpaceX%20and%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20take%20it%20as%20a%20given%20that%20two%20individuals%20by%20themselves%2C%20without%20outside%20assistance%2C%20will%20manage%20the%20supposed%20task%20of%20rooting%20out%20fraud%2C%20waste%2C%20and%20abuse%20in%20a%20system%20that%20handles%20over%20a%20billion%20payments%20a%20year%2C%20and%20trillions%20and%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20payments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20representing%20Bessent%20and%20the%20Treasury%20Department%2C%20Bradley%20P.%20Humphreys%2C%20countered%20during%20the%20hearing%20that%20only%20Elez%20had%20direct%20access%20to%20the%20data%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20briefs%20and%20reports%20to%20Mr.%20Krause%2C%20who%20does%20not%20have%20direct%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20those%20two%20individuals%20have%20been%20given%20any%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20Humphreys%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20special%20government%20employees%20of%20the%20Treasury%20Department%2C%20both%20were%20subject%20to%20federal%20ethics%20and%20confidentiality%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20they%20disseminated%20any%20of%20that%20information%20to%20anybody%20else%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20asked%20Humphreys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20we%20are%20aware%2C%20no%20they%20have%20not%2C%20outside%20of%20the%20Treasury%20Department%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20to%20Musk%2C%20Humphreys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20he%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20records%2C%20if%20he's%20not%20at%20Treasury%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20asked%20of%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20United%20States%20DOGE%20Service%2C%20and%20with%20the%20executive%20office%20of%20the%20president%2C%20as%20a%20special%20government%20employee%26quot%3B%20Humphreys%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20our%20understanding%20is%20that%20the%20information%20derived%20from%20the%20systems%20at%20issue%20in%20this%20case%20is%20not%20being%20transmitted%20to%20him%20outside%20of%20the%20Treasury%20Department%2C%26quot%3B%20Humphreys%20added%20of%20Musk.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20in%20the%20Treasury%20Department.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20he%20have%20access%20to%20it%3F%20Can%20he%20go%20look%20at%20it%3F%20Has%20he%20gone%20and%20looked%20at%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20your%20honor.%20To%20our%20knowledge%20he%20has%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Humphreys%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20had%20told%20the%20lawyers%20for%20both%20sides%20that%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20put%20an%20order%20in%20place%20that%20would%20keep%20it%20that%20way%2C%20with%20no%20one%20beyond%20Krause%20and%20Elez%20having%20access%20to%20the%20data%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sides%20were%20given%20until%206%20p.m.%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement%20on%20the%20language%20for%20the%20order.%20When%20they%20failed%20to%20reach%20that%20agreement%2C%20she%20told%20them%20to%20try%20again%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20like%20you're%20very%20close%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20wording%2C%20she%20told%20them%20when%20the%20parties%20reconvened%20at%206%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bessent%20lawsuit%20challenges%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20Treasury's%20ongoing%20release%20to%20DOGE%20of%20sensitive%20data%20from%20anyone%20who%20pays%20federal%20taxes%2C%20collects%20Social%20Security%2C%20or%20otherwise%20engages%20financially%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20unions%20asked%20to%20block%20the%20sharing%20of%20this%20Treasury%20data%20with%20DOGE%20while%20the%20lawsuit%20proceeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Treasury%20and%20Bessent%20%26quot%3Bhave%20unlawfully%20implemented%20and%20are%20unlawfully%20maintaining%20a%20system%20that%20enables%20records%20and%20information%20about%20individuals%20to%20be%20accessed%20and%20disclosed%20to%20unauthorized%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unions%20argue%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20the%20intrusion%20into%20individuals'%20privacy%20is%20massive%20and%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unions%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Retired%20Americans%2C%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Government%20Employees%2C%20AFL-CIO%2C%20and%20the%20Service%20Employees%20International%20Union%2C%20AFL-CIO.%20It%20alleges%20that%20releasing%20the%20names%20and%20financial%20details%20of%20pe