0and%20often%20lulls%20him%20to%20sleep.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20also%20likes%20listening%20to%20science-based%20cards%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqueen-fat-bottomed-girls-off-new-hits-album-controversy-explained-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYoto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20child-friendly%20audio%20platform.%20Doing%20so%20helps%20us%20get%20out%20the%20door%20faster%20as%20we%20get%20ready%20in%20the%20morning.%20Recently%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20%26quot%3BLadybird%20Audio%20Adventures%26quot%3B%20volcano%20card%2C%20which%20coordinates%20well%20with%20a%20book%20he's%20also%20enjoying%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20Inside%3A%20Volcanoes%20and%20Earthquakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226313e26b-0bc8-464d-b1a7-1f59d4228efa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20find%20science%20in%20everyday%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20son%20is%20already%20interested%20in%20science%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20apply%20the%20scientific%20method%20or%20scientific%20inquiry%20to%20everyday%20life.%20We'll%20often%20talk%20about%20things%20like%20the%20yeast%20in%20our%20sourdough%20starter%20or%20how%20to%20measure%20liquids%20properly%20in%20a%20measuring%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20favorite%20summer%20activities%20is%20gardening%3B%20he%20and%20my%20husband%20will%20plant%20a%20small%20assortment%20of%20vegetables%2C%20and%20he%20is%20thrilled%20to%20help%20care%20for%20and%20eat%20them.%20We%20discuss%20what%20the%20plants%20need%20to%20grow%20and%20how%20bees%20help%20pollinate%20certain%20plants.%20We%20even%20planted%20some%20tickle-me%20plants%20indoors%20%E2%80%94%20their%20leaves%20close%20up%20when%20they're%20touched%2C%20which%20is%20a%20defense%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObserving%20nature%20can%20be%20an%20experiment%20of%20itself%3B%20watching%20the%20raindrops%2C%20seeing%20how%20high%20the%20water%20splashes%20when%20jumping%20versus%20stepping%20in%20puddles%2C%20or%20watching%20the%20leaves%20