ter%20and%20ice%20as%20the%20children%20learn%20about%20how%20salt%20impacts%20melting%20point.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3dd92bfebcc4d029df1e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20of%20my%20kids%20enjoy%20this%20ice%20fishing%20experiment%20that%20shows%20how%20salt%20can%20impact%20the%20freezing%20point%20of%20ice.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0306ee3-a1a7-41d3-b230-2cdd92ab4e85%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20turn%20bath%20time%20into%20a%20fun%20experiment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%20son's%20Christmas%20stocking%20was%20stuffed%20with%20a%20few%20bath%20potions%20that%20have%20been%20a%20big%20hit.%20He%20has%20both%20powder%20and%20mini%20bath%20bomb%20cubes%20that%20fit%20inside%20of%20a%20flask.%20You%20pour%20warm%20water%20into%20the%20flask%20and%20it%20reacts%20to%20form%20a%20colorful%20mini%20volcano.%20My%20son%20took%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20pour%20some%20of%20the%20potion%20into%20another%20flask%20or%20take%20the%20cubes%20out.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe've%20reused%20the%20flask%20with%20bath%20color%20tablets%20and%20it%20resulted%20in%20a%20similar%20reaction%20(albeit%20smaller).%20He%20has%20fun%20playing%20pretend%20with%20the%20potions%2C%20often%20imitating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fwhere-to-watch-bluey-stream-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluey%20minisode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BStrong%20Potion%2C%26quot%3B%20asking%20me%20to%20buy%20his%20potions%20and%20choosing%20what%20animal%20they'll%20turn%20me%20into%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20cartoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22809c938a-685d-4448-9841-e84e980cfcfa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20embrace%20science%20and%20building%20kits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%2