%9D%20says%20Srinidhi.%20This%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20Aecoz%20in%202020%2C%20a%20boot-strapped%20startup%20focused%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20solutions%20for%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPackaging%20out%20of%20paper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%202019%20plastic%20ban%20may%20not%20have%20achieved%20its%20full%20potential%2C%20it%20served%20as%20a%20valuable%20catalyst%20for%20the%20development%20of%20biodegradable%20packaging%20alternatives%20for%20these%20entrepreneurs.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20%E2%80%98EatFit%E2%80%99%20(a%20food%20outlet%20catering%20to%20your%20diet)%2C%20who%20asked%20for%20biodegradable%20packaging.%20We%20took%20the%20challenge%20seriously%20and%20with%20a%20little%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20were%20successful%20in%20creating%20a%20durable%20yet%20sustainable%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhanvita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAecoz%E2%80%99s%20paper%20packaging%20production%20begins%20with%20sourcing%20paper%20reels%20from%20ITC%3B%20%E2%80%9CThey%20supply%20about%2085-90%25%20of%20the%20paper%20we%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Bharath%2C%20who%20oversees%20the%20manufacturing%20unit.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20reels%20are%20coated%20with%20a%20water-based%20barrier%2C%20making%20the%20paper%20suitable%20for%20food%20packaging.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-500x598.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aecoz%20packaging%20with%20Ritz%20Carlton%20branding.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-500x598.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-251x300.jpg%20251w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-150x180.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-402962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20packaging%20made%20by%20Aecoz%20is%2098%25%20biodegradable%20in%20180%20days.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20aqueous%20coating%20on%20our%20products%20makes%20the%20packaging%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270443%2Fchuk-biodegradable-compostable-waste-sugarcane-fibre-tableware%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E98%25%20biodegradable%20in%20180%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20certified%20by%20the%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Petrochemicals%20Engineering%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20(CIPET)%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dhanvita.%20The%20product%20has%20also%20received%20food%20grade%2C%20pollution%20and%20no-plastic%20certification%20from%20CIPET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reels%20are%20cut%20into%20blanks%20and%20formed%20into%20bowls.%20The%20bowls%20then%20pass%20through%20high-temperature%20coils%20reaching%20approximately%20350%C2%B0C%20to%20melt%20the%20coating%20and%20create%20a%20durable%2C%20heat-resistant%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20machine%20operates%20at%20an%20impressive%20speed%2C%20producing%2040-45%20pieces%20per%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharath%20informs.%20%E2%80%9CAecoz%20utilises%20specialised%20machines%20to%20produce%20various%20sizes%20from%2050%20ml%20to%201000%20ml%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20product%20meets%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20our%20clients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Aecoz%2C%20primarily%20dealing%20B2B%2C%20has%20produced%20and%20sold%20more%20than%204.5%20crore%20products%20like%20cups%2C%20bowls%2C%20containers%2C%20lids%2C%20boxes%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20providing%20an%20effective%20solution%20to%20microplastics%20and%20single-use%20plastics%2C%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20prevented%20the%20use%20of%20over%20four%20lakh%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%2C%20significantly%20reducing%20pollution%20in%20the%20food%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhanvita.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20Rs%205%20crore%20venture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20restaurants%20in%20India%20can%20afford%20to%20spend%20on%20packaging%2C%20which%20Aecoz%20also%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20target%20our%20products%20towards%20high-end%20customers%20who%20can%20afford%20the%2035%25%20increase%20in%20price%20when%20compared%20to%20plastic%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinidhi%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastic%20is%20a%20by-product.%20Paper%20is%20not%2C%20which%20influences%20the%20conversion%20cost.%20This%20gets%20reflected%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20our%20paper%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Srinidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20food%20brand%20MTR%20was%20Aecoz%E2%80%99s%20firs