r%20gardens%20and%20prioritise%20hiring%20locally%2C%20which%20helps%20uplift%20the%20regional%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20locale%20does%20make%20for%20an%20idyllic%20spot%2C%20it%20also%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20during%20the%20construction.%20Ankush%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20which%20we%20faced%20in%20this%20project%20was%20installing%20the%20bathtubs%20in%20the%20bathrooms.%20All%20the%20bathtubs%20are%20crafted%20out%20of%20a%20single%20piece%20of%20stone%20and%20are%20very%20heavy.%20There%20was%20no%20way%20for%20a%20crane%20to%20reach%20the%20place.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20property%20was%20conceived%20by%20two%20families%20from%20Gurugram%20who%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20their%20children%20could%20grow%20up%20in%20nature%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fglasshouse-celeste-4-1738067379-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-401521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20property%20was%20conceived%20by%20two%20families%20from%20Gurugram%20who%20were%20